text: Münchenbuchsee is a municipality in the administrative district of Bern- Mittelland in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. It is famous as the birthplace of painter Paul Klee. Since 2023, Diemerswil became a part of Münchenbuchsee. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Bern-Mittelland
title: Münchenbuchsee
